title: Fasion Photography
details: In the simplest of terms, I am a portrait photographer. My work spans the advertising, editorial, music, and entertainment worlds.I found photography in my early thirties after more than a decade as a chef and restaurateur.  Finding beauty in simplicity has been the driving force throughout my entire working life. Much in the way food connects us, I seek to portray connection through the photographs I make.I was raised in the Low Country of South Carolina and after spending nearly a decade in NYC, I currently reside with my wife and creative partner, Monique, in the foothills of the Sierra Nevada Mountains in California.
